<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1080625968">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1080625968" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1080625968" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1080625968">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/conscience/">种瓜得瓜</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">粗粗翻阅一过，像我这样的非专业研究者真没必要读。季羡林自述本书的着眼点在中外交流史的考察，国内编除了胪列由浩如烟海的正史笔记类书中捞出来的史料，就是怨念深深的吐槽，按语不多，或许是不得不写却其实又兴趣不高。而一到国外编，殊然迥异，火力全开。涉及琉球事写的很多，对此有兴趣的读者可一读。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="349026010">
        <div class="comment">
